Simple Yet Attractive Restaurant Landing Page
Project Description
This project showcases a minimalist and visually appealing landing page for a restaurant, designed solely with HTML and CSS. The objective is to create an engaging user experience with a clean layout, vibrant colors, and responsive design, highlighting key restaurant features such as menu offerings, special promotions, location, and contact information.

Technologies Used
HTML5: Structuring the content and layout of the landing page.
CSS3: Styling the page, including the use of Flexbox and Grid for layout, and animations for enhanced user interaction.

Contributing
Contributions are welcome! If you have suggestions for improvements or want to add new features, feel free to fork the repository and submit a pull request.

